<Link id="l00169" /><CodeLine lineNumber="169"><Highlight kind="comment">  ///</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00170" /><CodeLine lineNumber="170"><Highlight kind="comment">  /// When comparing InlineInfo objects the item with the most inline functions</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00171" /><CodeLine lineNumber="171"><Highlight kind="comment">  /// wins. If we have two FunctionInfo objects that both have the same address</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00172" /><CodeLine lineNumber="172"><Highlight kind="comment">  /// range and both have valid InlineInfo objects, we want the one with the</Highlight></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00175" /><CodeLine lineNumber="175"><Highlight kind="comment">  /// function information for the same address range, so this helps ensure we</Highlight></CodeLine>
